5 SECTION 2. Arkansas Code ยง 17-101-319(b)(3), concerning indirect
6 supervision of veterinary technician specialists by a veterinarian, is
7 amended to read as follows:
8 (3)(A) A veterinarian who utilizes indirect supervision of a
